title: USA Championships - Day 4
description: O'Neill Team continued to advance in the building swell down at Lowers. Dylan Walsh, Kain Daly, Ian Crane competed in the Boys Under 18 division while Jasset Umbel and Kiana Fores competed in the Girls Under 18 division.
